== Edit request 1 March 2026: Do not mention Harvard in the infobox ==

The infobox currently lists Harvard University as part of Netanyahu’s education, but this overemphasizes the affiliation. He was not enrolled as a degree-seeking student at Harvard; rather, he attended a limited number of courses made available through the MIT/Harvard collaboration. Such brief and non-degree participation does not constitute a substantive academic association. Given the minor and incidental nature of this connection, including Harvard in the infobox overstates its significance and should be removed. [[User:Ramanujaner|Ramanujaner]] ([[User talk:Ramanujaner|talk]]) 09:33, 1 March 2026 (UTC)

